ion.getBrokers();\\n        }\\n    }\\n\\n    private static final class ClientIdMockProducer extends MockProducer<Object, Object> {\\n        private final String clientId = FIELD_CLIENT_ID;\\n    }\\n}\\n\"}\nhuman-intervention-logs/org.apache.camel:camel-kafka:4.20.0/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-05-08T00-20-49-601450Z.log:2163:[tool-call] end id=call_XPXrzVWgYXt1MQOCPeAFDrAS|fc_0b589c16a8154e9c0169fd2c361084819d8551f367908eaae4 name=write args={\"path\": \"tests/src/org.apache.camel/camel-kafka/4.20.0/src/test/java/org_apache_camel/camel_kafka/KafkaProducerTest.java\", \"content\": \"/*\\n * Copyright and related rights waived via CC0\\n *\\n * You should have received a copy of the CC0 legalcode along with this\\n * work. If not, see <http://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/>.\\n */\\npackage org_apache_camel.camel_kafka;\\n\\nimport java.time.Duration;\\nimport java.util.Properties;\\n\\nimport org.apache.camel.Producer;\\nimport org.apache.camel.component.kafka.KafkaClientFactory;\\nimport org.apache.camel.component.kafka.KafkaComponent;\\nimport org.apache.camel.component.kafka.KafkaConfiguration;\\nimport org.apache.camel.component.kafka.KafkaEndpoint;\\nimport org.apache.camel.impl.DefaultCamelContext;\\nimport org.apache.kafka.clients.consumer.Consumer;\\nimport org.apache.kafka.clients.producer.MockProducer;\\nimport org.apache.kafka.clients.producer.ProducerConfig;\\nimport org.apache.kafka.common.serialization.StringSerializer;\\nimport org.junit.jupiter.api.Test;\\n\\nimport static org.assertj.core.api.Assertions.assertThat;\\n\\npublic class KafkaProducerTest {\\n\\n    private static final String BROKERS = \\\"localhost:65535\\\";\\n    private static final String FIELD_CLIENT_ID = \\\"client-id-from-producer-field\\\";\\n\\n    @Test\\n    void startReadsClientIdFromKafkaProducerFieldWhenPropertyIsAbsent() throws Exception {\\n        FieldClientIdKafkaClientFactory clientFactory = new FieldClientIdKafkaClientFactory();\\n   